Uses of Interface
com.deliburd.extrataskschedulers.CallbackFuture

    • Uses of CallbackFuture in com.deliburd.extrataskschedulers

      Subinterfaces of CallbackFuture in com.deliburd.extrataskschedulers 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  StealingCallbackFuture<V>
      A Future that has methods to do work in the executor linked to it while waiting for a computation's result.
      Classes in com.deliburd.extrataskschedulers that implement CallbackFuture 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  StealingCallbackFutureTask<V>
      A FutureTask that can do work in the executor linked to it if one is provided and can have work stolen from it while waiting for a computation's result.
      Methods in com.deliburd.extrataskschedulers that return CallbackFuture 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      CallbackFuture<?> CallbackExecutorService.submit​(Runnable task)
      Submits a task that returns null to the returned CallbackFuture when it's done.
      <T> CallbackFuture<T> CallbackExecutorService.submit​(Runnable task, T result)
      Submits a task that returns the given result to the returned CallbackFuture when it's done.
      <T> CallbackFuture<T> CallbackExecutorService.submit​(Callable<T> task)
      Submits a task that returns a value to the returned CallbackFuture when it's done.
